        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-07",
        "text": "From the Hip knocked it out of the park for our wedding in June! Lauren was very responsive in the planning process and developing a package that met our needs. My husband doesn’t like having his photo taken and they were able to accommodate a smaller time package and still get incredible photos of us. Brooke was so sweet, captured beautiful moments of us, and understanding when we were ready to be done with photos. They delivered our photos back within the advertised 4 week turnaround! Thank you Brooke and Lauren for a wonderful experience!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2021-01",
        "text": "We booked with From the Hip for both our maternity and newborn photos and are very happy we did! Lauren is very professional and responsive during the planning phase and Julia did a wonderful job on our photos. They were both very kind and flexible when we had to reschedule day of due to unexpected scheduling issues on our end. Then the day of, we had to change locations at the last minute due to weather but Julia came up with a perfect back up plan and we are thrilled with how the photos turned out. I would highly recommend this team and look forward to capturing our baby girl with them in a few more weeks! Thank you!"
      },
      {
